    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随笔—观怒吟</title>
      <link>https://www.xiaoledeng.com/2025/01/11/guannu-yin/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 16:38:50 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.xiaoledeng.com/2025/01/11/guannu-yin/</guid>
      <description>一言不合已发飙，怒气冲冲意难平；&#xA;言语急躁起争端，伤己伤人亦伤情。&#xA;怒气初始即逃避，相守相伴贵和气；&#xA;谦卑心安常敬畏，智慧行事伏己心。</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随笔—观痛吟</title>
